Class VltpackServerSideTestBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.adamcin.commons.testing.sling.VltpackServerSideTestBase
  • Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class VltpackServerSideTestBase
extends Object
    Test server-side tests using the Sling JUnit servlet, as opposed to the plain JUnit servlet. Deprecated in favor of graniteit-maven-plugin and SlingRemoteTestBase
